highlights.text: “Kepuraanmu” by Luqman Faiz is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Malaysia, up 74 spots at #119.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Top Songs Malaysia. “Golden” is the highest at #1.
“Night Changes” by One Direction has been on Top Songs Malaysia the longest, at 1683 days straight.
“Jealous Type” by Doja Cat is the highest new entry on Top Songs Malaysia at #83.
